    <description>Mixins.Helper is a basic and useful collection of Less Mixins Functions that are used to redeuce the work needed to apply styling to elements and cross-browser CSS compatibility. Mixins.Helper comes with a visual studio and microsoft friendly NuGet package.</description>
    <summary>Mixins.Helper is a basic and useful collection of Less Mixins Functions that are used to redeuce the work needed to apply styling to elements and cross-browser CSS compatibility.</summary>
